OL,3,CAssociate of Manchester synagogue
OL,4,Cattacker planned MoD terror attack,
OL,5,Ccourt told
OL,7,FA "long-standing, committed jihadist"
OL,8,Fplanned a terror attack on a military
OL,9,Fsite with the man who went on to
OL,10,Fcommit a fatal knife attack at a
OL,11,FManchester synagogue, a court has
OL,12,Fheard.
OL,14,FMohammed Bashir, 31, drove Jihad Al-
OL,15,FShamie, 35, on a 10-hour round trip to
OL,16,Fconduct hostile reconnaissance at the
OL,17,FUK Defence Academy in Shrivenham,
OL,18,FSwindon, on 14 August last year before
OL,19,Fthey deliberately disposed of their
OL,20,Fmobile phones.
