OL,3,CAssociate of Manchester synagogue
OL,4,Cattacker planned MoD terror attack,
OL,5,Ccourt told
OL,7,FLess than two months later, Al-Shamie
OL,8,Fwas shot dead by police on 2 October
OL,9,Fwhile he carried out his terrorist
OL,10,Fattack at the Heaton Park Hebrew
OL,11,FCongregation synagogue in which two
OL,12,Fworshippers were killed.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G2/7
