OL,3,CAssociate of Manchester synagogue
OL,4,Cattacker planned MoD terror attack,
OL,5,Ccourt told
OL,7,FFollowing the attack, WhatsApp
OL,8,Fmessages and voice note exchanges
OL,9,Fbetween the pair were uncovered when
OL,10,Fpolice analysed two phones seized from
OL,11,FAl-Shamie when he was arrested in
OL,12,FFebruary 2025 over an alleged breach
OL,13,Fof a non-molestation order and in
OL,14,FSeptember 2025 when he was held on
OL,15,Fsuspicion of rape, Manchester Crown
OL,16,FCourt heard.
OL,18,FProsecutor Jonathan Polnay KC said:
OL,19,F"The prosecution case is that Mohammad
OL,20,FBashir is a long-standing, committed
OL,21,Fjihadist.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G3/7
