PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F362A1784834318
OL,3,CAssociate of Manchester synagogue
OL,4,Cattacker planned MoD terror attack,
OL,5,Ccourt told
OL,7,F"The attack that was being planned was
OL,8,Fof the sort that Jihad Al-Shamie in
OL,9,Ffact carried out on October 2, an
OL,10,Fattack involving weapons that would
OL,11,Fcause multiple fatalities and have
OL,12,Fnational and international impact.
OL,14,F"Analysis of Bashir and Al-Shamie's
OL,15,Fmessages to each other demonstrated
OL,16,Fthey were both close associates and
OL,17,Fboth shared an extremist worldview.
OL,19,F"They were both interested in, and
OL,20,Fregularly discussed, violent jihad."
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G4/7
