OL,3,CAssociate of Manchester synagogue
OL,4,Cattacker planned MoD terror attack,
OL,5,Ccourt told
OL,7,FLast month, Bashir, of Shaftesbury
OL,8,FRoad, Cheetham, pleaded guilty to the
OL,9,Fpreparation of terrorist acts.
OL,11,FManchester-born Bashir, who also holds
OL,12,Fa Pakistani passport, has no previous
OL,13,Fconvictions.
OL,15,FBashir was arrested at Manchester
OL,16,FAirport on 27 November but was not
OL,17,Fcharged in relation to the synagogue
OL,18,Fattack.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G5/7
