OL,3,CAssociate of Manchester synagogue
OL,4,Cattacker planned MoD terror attack,
OL,5,Ccourt told
OL,7,FMelvin Cravitz, 66, and Adrian Daulby,
OL,8,F53, died after Al-Shamie, a Syrian-
OL,9,Fborn UK citizen, drove his Kia Picanto
OL,10,Finto the gates of the synagogue and
OL,11,Fbegan attacking with a knife, wearing
OL,12,Fa fake suicide belt.
OL,14,FMoD Shrivenham is the home of the UK
OL,15,FDefence Academy, the court heard,
OL,16,Fwhich provides professional defence
OL,17,Fand security education to the British
OL,18,FArmed Forces, wider UK government, UK
OL,19,Findustry and overseas personnel.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G6/7
